column5: I can zone out on tik tok for hours and because it's tailored to your likes and I only like positive stuff Its a happy place for me.
This gave me chills. Thank you for putting these feelings into words.
This is painfully close to the way I feel. I'm sorry I have nothing to offer other than to say that you're not alone.
But then do you ever stop to think if you're really doing it out of the goodness of your heart or if you have other motives? Cause I do that. I always doubt my intentions.
Sex work is valid as long as you consent and feel good about it. Maybe sit with your emotions on this and see what feelings develop before you do it again.
